Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.69,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Počúvam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:06.93,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno, tiež si myslím.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.29,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Veľmi sa ospravedlňujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.04,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Len som si v hlave predstavoval,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.01,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,čo mi práve hovoríš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.67,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Teraz mlčí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.21,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Ale neviem, ako dlho to potrvá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.58,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Rozumiem.\NUvidíme sa neskôr.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.90,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Nepozvaný hosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:55.37,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Alebo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.44,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,... vítaný...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.08,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,... hosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:01.87,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Uvidíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.30,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Démon! Poď tadiaľto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.07,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Kam kývam rukou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.54,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Hovoríš, že si k nám zostúpil z diery?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:42.74,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.21,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Sám?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:46.89,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.71,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.42,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.97,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Prišiel si v zlých časoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.42,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Ran, schovaj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.40,Text,Comment,0,0,0,,Duša! Telo! Pravda!\NSpása! Pomsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:38.53,Ending,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Oslnivé biele tričko,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:49.24,Ending,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}dúha v kvapkách vody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:22:00.57,Ending,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Ničota bola naším šťastím.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:10.78,Ending,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Klesám hlbšie, než ktokoľvek iný.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:21.27,Ending,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}A teraz tu hľadím len na teba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:31.81,Ending,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Ak je to sen, ktorý sa už nikdy nevráti, zničím ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:37.81,Ending,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Nedokážem na teba zabudnúť,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:44.72,Ending,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}chcem ťa znovu stretnúť.
